	oking-class-1pm/?occurrence=2026-03-16&time=1773666000
LOCATION:Atrium Kitchen\, 93 Pike St\, Seattle\, WA 98101
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
