BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:4ixexAYQpo8LfpEvo8XYI
SUMMARY:Author Talk: Claudia Rowe discusses "Wards of the State: The Long S
	hadow of American Foster Care"
DTSTAMP:20260315T214141Z
DTSTART:20260320T013000Z
DESCRIPTION:Rowe's reporting on racially skewed school discipline for The S
	eattle Times helped to change education laws in Washington State\, and her
